Subject: Re: How to encrypt voice skype calls?

instead of focusing the discussion on Skype - which is not open and
proprietary - we should use the standard VoIP protocols such as SIP or
similar. Encryption is readily available for standard VoIP protocols and
there are also alternatives such as zrtp ...


